	<h1 class="title">能帮你算吃了多少卡路里的应用为啥被嫌弃了？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/101671/small/101671.jpg?1455867778" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">潘姜汐熹 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-15 09:36:29 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/9612/medium/9612.jpg?1436675415" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="9612" data-title="《能帮你算吃了多少卡路里的应用为啥被嫌弃了？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/9612/medium/9612.jpg?1436675415" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/9612.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
